Subject: Re: [RFC][PATCH] x86_64:  Fix collision between pmtimer and pit/hpet timekeeping
Sender: linux-kernel-owner@vger.kernel.org
Precedence: bulk
List-ID: <linux-kernel.vger.kernel.org>
